#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.expit.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.expit"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.expit:1 of
msgid "Expit (a.k.a. logistic sigmoid) ufunc for ndarrays."
msgstr "用于ndarrays的Expit（也称为logistic sigmoid）ufunc。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.expit:3 of
msgid ""
"The expit function, also known as the logistic sigmoid function, is "
"defined as ``expit(x) = 1/(1+exp(-x))``.  It is the inverse of the logit "
"function."
msgstr ""
"expit函数，也称为logistic sigmoid函数，定义为 ``expit(x) = 1/(1+exp(-x))`"
"`。它是logit函数的反函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.expit of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.expit:7 of
msgid "The ndarray to apply expit to element-wise."
msgstr "要逐元素应用expit的ndarray。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.expit:9 of
msgid "Optional output array for the function values"
msgstr "函数值的可选输出数组"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.expit of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.expit:12 of
msgid ""
"An ndarray of the same shape as x. Its entries are `expit` of the "
"corresponding entry of x."
msgstr "与x形状相同的ndarray。其条目是x对应条目的`expit`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.expit of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.expit:18 of
msgid ":func:`logit`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.expit:22 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.expit:23 of
msgid ""
"As a ufunc expit takes a number of optional keyword arguments. For more "
"information see `ufuncs "
"<https://docs.scipy.org/doc/numpy/reference/ufuncs.html>`_"
msgstr ""
"作为ufunc，expit接受一些可选关键字参数。更多信息请参见 `ufuncs <https://"
"docs.scipy.org/doc/numpy/reference/ufuncs.html>`_"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.statistical.expit:27 of
msgid ""
"`expit` has experimental support for Python Array API Standard compatible"
" backends in addition to NumPy. Please consider testing these features by"
" setting an environment variable ``SCIPY_ARRAY_API=1`` and providing "
"CuPy, PyTorch, JAX, or Dask arrays as array arguments. The following "
"combinations of backend and device (or other capability) are supported."
msgstr ""
"`expit`除了NumPy之外，还对Python Array API Standard兼容的后端有实验性支持"
"。请考虑通过设置环境变量``SCIPY_ARRAY_API=1``并提供CuPy、PyTorch、JAX或"
"Dask数组作为数组参数来测试这些功能。支持以下后端和设备（或其他能力）的"
"组合。"

